        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Study broadens your range of simple spells.   \n  \n**Prepared Caster (Cleric, Wizard, etc.)**: You can prepare two additional cantrips each day.  \n**Spontaneous Caster (Bard, Sorcerer, etc.)**: Add two additional cantrips from your spell list to your repertoire.",
